# Awesome Agentic Reasoning Papers [![Awesome](https://awesome.re/badge.svg)](https://awesome.re)

A curated list of papers on **Agentic Reasoning for Large Language Models**. This repository organizes papers by topics related to planning, tool-use, search, self-evolution, multi-agent systems, and applications.

> ğŸ“„ **Based on the survey**: *Agentic Reasoning for Large Language Models: A Survey*

